<h2>The Transition Property</h2>
<p>
    A demo paragraph, often referred to as "Lorem Ipsum" or placeholder text, is used in design and development to visualize how content will appear within a layout. It allows designers and developers to focus on the visual aspects of a project without being distracted by the actual content. This helps in assessing spacing, font choices, and overall design aesthetics. 

